tion></figure><p>在麦当娜的其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-is-back-in-the-studio-in-london-working-with-stuart-price-3799284">她最近证实她回到了伦敦的录音室</a>，并再次与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stuart-price">斯图尔特·普莱斯 (Stuart Price</a> ) 合作，斯图尔特·普莱斯是她 2005 年专辑《Confessions On A Dance Floor》等的联合制作人。</p><p>如果他们正在制作的新材料最终成为一张新专辑，这将成为麦当娜自 2019 年发行<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/madonna-madame-x-review-2505126">《Madame X》</a>以来的第一张 LP。</p><p>本月早些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonnas-brother-christopher-ciccone-dies-aged-63-3799975">她的兄弟 Christopher Ciccone 因癌症去世，享年 63 岁</a>。</p><p>克里斯托弗在姐姐职业生涯的早期就与她密切合作，在她 1990 年的 Blond Ambition 世界巡演中担任艺术总监，并在 1993 年的 The Girlie Show 巡演中担任巡演总监。</p><p>麦当娜<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-tribute-late-brother-christopher-closest-human-to-me-for-so-long-3799996">向他表示敬意</a>，称他为“这么长时间以来与我最亲近的人”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/madonna-shares-endorsement-for-kamala-harris-3808708">麦当娜为卡玛拉·哈里斯代言的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
英国草根场馆遭受“巡演彻底崩溃”之苦——以下是您可以提供帮助的方法https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-grassroots-music-venues-touring-collapse-mvt-steve-lamacq-budget-help-3808675?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=uk-grassroots-music-场馆巡演崩溃-MVT-史蒂夫-拉马克-预算-帮助Andrew TrendellFri, 01 Nov 2024 14:55:45 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3808675 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="史蒂夫·拉马克 (Steve Lamacq) 出席音乐场馆信托基金 2024 年场馆日活动。图片来源：Georgia Penny" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在预算受到打击之后，艺术家们无力承担演出费用，全国各地的演出也减少了，现场音乐再次处于“当下的 30 分钟可能改变未来”的生存损失的边缘。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-grassroots-music-venues-touring-collapse-mvt-steve-lamacq-budget-help-3808675">英国草根场馆遭受“巡演彻底崩溃”之苦——以下是你可以如何帮助的方法</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="史蒂夫·拉马克 (Steve Lamacq) 出席音乐场馆信托基金 2024 年场馆日活动。图片来源：Georgia Penny" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/music_venues_day_24_opening_1_Georgia-Penny-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由于最近的预算消息和整个行业未能做出反应，英国草根音乐界的巡回演出据说在没有紧急帮助的情况下面临“彻底崩溃”。</p><p>在过去的一年里，英国较小的场馆和新兴艺术家面临着越来越大的压力，他们需要从竞技场和体育场的演出中获得捐款，以确保他们的生存。该模型与英超联赛中的模型类似，并且已经在欧洲多个国家使用， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/industry-reacts-as-mps-recommend-ticket-levy-on-arenas-and-stadiums-to-save-grassroots-venues-and-artists-3755386">早在春季 DCMS 进行调查后，议员们就推荐了</a>该模型。</p><p>酷玩乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-coldplay-ticket-money-donation-interview-3798462">(Coldplay)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-case-has-been-made-for-a-1-ticket-levy-on-all-arena-gigs-for-the-survival-of-grassroots-venues-and-artists-3611533">Enter Shikari</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-uk-european-people-watching-tour-buy-tickets-3803992">Sam Fender 等公司都在大型巡演中征收了自己的税，</a>以帮助拯救草根阶层，但政府和行业高层的不作为仍然令人沮丧——而且压力只会越来越大，在本周的预算公布后，政府似乎对这一呼吁置若罔闻。</p><p>尽管<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/report-shows-disaster-facing-grassroots-music-venues-the-big-companies-and-arenas-are-now-going-to-have-to-answer-for-this-3576307">2023 年被证明是“灾难性的”，也是有记录以来最糟糕的一年，有 125 个草根音乐场所关门</a>，但 MVT 认为，由于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-uk-autumn-budget-music-industry-reacts-with-venues-and-nightclubs-at-risk-3808036">最近的预算公告，</a>关闭浪潮威胁着英国音乐界的结构。他们认为，700 万英镑的新场地税将使 350 多个草根音乐场所面临直接关闭的风险，从而威胁到超过 12,000 个就业岗位、超过 2.5 亿英镑的经济活动以及超过 75,000 场现场音乐活动的损失。</p><p> MVT 在一份声明中表示：“十多年来，围绕商业价格和草根音乐场所的挑战已为人所知并接受。” “2026 年 4 月的变化值得欢迎，但对于数百个音乐场所来说毫无用处，在最终通过全面的、早该进行的改革来应对这一挑战之前，这些音乐场所现在可能会消失。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DBwaGFZNZqy/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.